  "bio_raw": "Dewan Shahnoor Alam Sourav is a media professional with diverse experience across journalism, broadcasting, and communications. He has worked with leading organizations, including The Data Owl, Newsquest Media Group, Sky News UK, Dhaka Tribune, and Business Insider, covering a wide range of reporting areas such as business, national, and crime news. Alongside journalism, he has gained cross-sector experience in Artificial Intelligence, hospitality,healthcare, media management, reflecting adaptability and strong interpersonal skills. Sourav holds an MA in Broadcast and Digital Journalism International from the University of East Anglia and a BSS in Media Studies and Journalism from the University of Liberal Arts Bangladesh. His expertise spans digital storytelling, generative AI, news features, multimedia production, and social media content creation. Bilingual in English and Bengali, he demonstrates the ability to work both independently and collaboratively in multicultural settings, delivering impactful stories and insights through high-quality reporting and data-driven analysis.",
  "stated_interests": [
    "Generative Ai, Augmented reality (AR),  Data Visualization, Sonification, Interactive storytelling, and Digital Journalism"
  ],
